<br>
For instance, I am now leveling on golra island.  These guys double attack for 60.  And often times they just ignore the pets and go straight for me.  To combat this, I use earth.  The root saves my but so much.  It is true that earth gets hit a lot, but throw a DS and work it for your advantage.  So basically for smart MOBs I use earth pet and his root as they tend to ignore the pet. <br>
